{"tid":2204653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"基因測序試劑被控侵權 華大承諾只供應現有本地客、限測試量 直至有判決","createTime":"2020-09-16T08:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T08:18:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"656a39138c6e7dc8a3621d5f0274ee4066fb6ca5","tid":2204653,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"有份負責「全民測試」的內地檢測機構華大基因多家關連公司，遭英國生物科技公司 Illumina 入稟控告其基因測序試劑套裝侵犯專利，案件今日（16日）在高等法院處理，華大一方自願承諾，只向現有本地客戶供應涉案測序儀及測序試劑，不尋找新客；華大透過香港轉運相關貨品予海外客戶的貨品，會原封不動；華大在香港繼續提供涉案基因測試程序，但將測序量（volume）限制在特定水平，不能測試更多，上述承諾有效直至案件有判決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%B8%AC%E5%BA%8F%E8%A9%A6%E5%8A%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A-%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E5%8F%AA%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E7%8F%BE%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2-%E9%99%90%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E9%87%8F-%E7%9B%B4%E8%87%B3%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E5%25BA%258F%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%258A%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E5%258F%25AA%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E9%2599%2590%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E9%2587%258F-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E8%2587%25B3%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25B1%25BA%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=a4ca1617\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E5%25BA%258F%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%258A%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E5%258F%25AA%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E9%2599%2590%25E6%2